Color
: Overall pale pink, with very narrow orange stripe in midline of rostrum, behind each eye straightly extending posteriorly to between gastric and branchial regions, and along upper margin of pterygostomian flap; antennal flagellum orange (

Poupin & Corbari 2016: fig. 9b; 
Fig. 23
B, reproduced by permission of J. Poupin

